# Pretvia — Project Overview

Next.js 16 App Router project with React 19, TypeScript, MongoDB, and Tailwind CSS.

## Tech Stack

- **Framework:** Next.js 16 (App Router), React 19, TypeScript 5.7
- **Database:** MongoDB via `getDb()` from `lib/mongodb.ts`
- **Auth:** JWT in httpOnly cookies (jose), bcrypt passwords — `lib/auth.ts`
- **Data fetching:** SWR (client), fetchers in `lib/swr-utils.ts`
- **UI:** shadcn/ui (Radix) in `components/ui/`, Tailwind CSS, Framer Motion
- **Package manager:** pnpm

## Directory Layout

```
app/              # Pages, layouts, API routes (App Router)
app/api/          # REST API route handlers
components/ui/    # shadcn/ui primitives (Button, Dialog, etc.)
components/dashboard/  # Feature components (logs, filters, sidebar, etc.)
hooks/            # Custom React hooks (use-auth, use-require-auth, etc.)
lib/              # Shared server/client utilities (auth, db, constants)
types/            # Shared TypeScript types (types/dashboard.ts)
```

## Import Alias

All imports use `@/*` mapped to the project root:

```ts
import { Button } from "@/components/ui/button";
import type { LogEntry } from "@/types/dashboard";
import { getSession } from "@/lib/auth";
```
